  "title": "FURC (Fabric Universal Remote Control)",
  "description": "The remote to control them all. With great power comes great responsibility.",
  "body": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/FURC2/BH_FURC_Header.png\" alt=\"header\" width=\"1903\" height=\"333\" /><em><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">The one remote to control them all.</span> <br /><br /></em>Shift + Right Click <span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">your favorite block to suddenly be able to access/control it from anywhere.<br /></span></strong></span></p>\n<p><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Examples of how to use:</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Sync to a lever to remotely control the lever.</strong></span></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Sync to a crafting table for a remote crafter.</strong></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Sync to a furnace to smelt your ores on the go.</strong></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Sync to your your favorite modded block to access it anywhere you desire.</strong></span>\n<ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>The possibilities are endless!</strong></span><br /><br /><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/FURC2/BH_FURC_Recipe.png\" alt=\"recipe\" width=\"1920\" height=\"193\" />\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; float: left;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RcFfzIz.png\" alt=\"remote\" width=\"603\" height=\"266\" /></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><em>*Energy version of remote available without recipe. You must give it a recipe or spawn it in.</em> </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/FURC2/BH_FURC_Features.png\" alt=\"features\" width=\"1920\" height=\"193\" /></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Better compatibility with other mods. (Please report any issues with other modded blocks on discord)</strong></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Suggest something in the discord below!</strong></span><br /><br /><a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/FURC2/BH_FURC_PromoCard.png\" alt=\"promo\" width=\"1920\" height=\"337\" /></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br /><a href=\"https://discord.gg/gjfJnmEy5r\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/FURC/BH_FURC_Discord.png\" alt=\"discord\" width=\"1920\" height=\"192\" /></a><br /><a href=\"https://discord.gg/gjfJnmEy5r\"><br /><br /></a></p>",
